http://www.sohu.com/a/430927064_100161026	34572
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/1fb0fd7873b8449e9bd0701dc755e758.jpeg" img_width="600" img_height="800" /></p>
<p>硬化前的道路。</p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201110/6308a18faa794f8b85d1ca9caa4ec65b.jpeg" img_width="600" img_height="800" /></p>
